WEBVTT

00:00:59.315 --> 00:01:05.170
I told Kang Jae Seong to admit to the slush fund.

00:01:05.170 --> 00:01:09.903
The company was bleeding cash, while he lined his own pockets.

00:01:09.903 --> 00:01:12.734
I just told him to turn himself in.

00:01:12.734 --> 00:01:15.547
So he planned the kidnapping.

00:01:16.967 --> 00:01:21.284
Do you have proof he created

00:01:21.284 --> 00:01:25.717
Choiseong Trading's slush fund?

00:01:26.797 --> 00:01:29.247
<i>The Audit team investigated</i>

00:01:29.247 --> 00:01:33.125
<i>Trading and Chemicals on Lee Sang Jae's orders, right?</i>

00:01:33.125 --> 00:01:34.084
[Team Leader Jo, Audit]

00:01:34.084 --> 00:01:36.186
<i>How's it going?</i>

00:01:37.054 --> 00:01:40.713
<i>Where are those files now?</i>

00:01:40.713 --> 00:01:42.523
<i>I destroyed them all.</i>

00:01:42.523 --> 00:01:44.043
<i>Chairman Kang ordered it.</i>

00:01:44.043 --> 00:01:45.164
<i>Yeah?</i>

00:01:45.164 --> 00:01:47.637
<i>They're completely unrecoverable?</i>

00:01:50.514 --> 00:01:54.560
<i>You must think I'm a pushover.</i>

00:01:57.336 --> 00:01:58.600
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:00.514
<i>I wasn't planning anything.</i>

00:02:00.514 --> 00:02:03.300
<i>- I'll destroy them right away. - Recover them.</i>

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:05.674
<i>Only the Trading data.</i>

00:02:06.674 --> 00:02:09.467
<i>Delete the Chemicals files for good.</i>

00:02:10.234 --> 00:02:13.580
<i>Prove we're on the same side,</i>

00:02:14.267 --> 00:02:18.219
<i>and I'll make you a division head someday.</i>

00:02:22.646 --> 00:02:25.017
These are Choiseong's internal audit files.

00:02:25.017 --> 00:02:31.474
I think he used Director Song, who's now missing, to create the slush fund.

00:02:32.681 --> 00:02:35.440
Start digging there.

00:02:38.434 --> 00:02:41.205
Why drag my wife into this?

00:02:41.205 --> 00:02:42.812
We'll find out soon enough.

00:02:42.812 --> 00:02:46.547
A wife or her family is the go-to place to hide dirty money.

00:02:46.547 --> 00:02:49.219
Where's Director Song now?

00:02:49.219 --> 00:02:51.651
He screwed me over too!

00:02:51.651 --> 00:02:54.322
The evidence keeps piling up.

00:02:54.322 --> 00:02:58.891
The Audit team's files were pretty thorough.

00:02:58.891 --> 00:03:00.275
You're not going anywhere.

00:03:00.275 --> 00:03:01.981
You know...

00:03:01.981 --> 00:03:04.505
Kang Jae Gyeong set me up!

00:03:04.505 --> 00:03:06.951
She faked the evidence and silenced the press.

00:03:06.951 --> 00:03:10.017
You're all being played!

00:03:24.939 --> 00:03:28.103
Why take it this far?

00:03:28.103 --> 00:03:32.192
You two pushed me this far.

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:40.043
Kang Jae Gyeong!

00:03:40.043 --> 00:03:42.204
Hey! Are you okay?

00:03:53.549 --> 00:03:55.775
What? Something wrong?

00:03:57.610 --> 00:04:00.230
No. It's nothing.

00:04:00.230 --> 00:04:04.113
<i>Maybe my heart rate spiked during treatment.</i>

00:04:04.113 --> 00:04:05.254
[Lee Sang Jae]

00:04:07.187 --> 00:04:09.533
<i>Where are you, sir?</i>

00:04:34.452 --> 00:04:35.851
Get off me!

00:04:36.652 --> 00:04:37.886
Let go!

00:04:38.605 --> 00:04:39.918
Let go!

00:05:03.693 --> 00:05:05.929
[Choiseong Trading CEO Kang Jae Seong's Strong Leadership]

00:05:16.506 --> 00:05:18.865
Are you all right?

00:05:18.865 --> 00:05:20.740
Bang Geul was worried.

00:05:20.740 --> 00:05:25.033
He... may wake up.

00:05:25.033 --> 00:05:27.631
Nurse Song says he's responding well.

00:05:27.631 --> 00:05:32.831
Then will you be back in your own body soon?

00:05:32.831 --> 00:05:36.524
I'm not sure. But we can help each other.

00:05:37.743 --> 00:05:45.440
The Audit team leader must've restored the files for Kang Jae Gyeong.

00:05:45.440 --> 00:05:48.432
- I'm sorry. - This isn't your fault.

00:05:48.432 --> 00:05:51.369
Jae Gyeong did this.

00:05:51.369 --> 00:05:53.669
Don't blame yourself.

00:06:08.054 --> 00:06:09.538
You're here.

00:06:09.538 --> 00:06:11.563
How's Jae Gyeong?

00:06:11.563 --> 00:06:14.376
Just a few scrapes.

00:06:14.376 --> 00:06:20.093
But I'm worried she is taking this too far.

00:06:20.093 --> 00:06:24.695
Chairman Kang is getting better, right?

00:06:25.434 --> 00:06:28.885
Yeah, the treatment is working.

00:06:28.885 --> 00:06:30.992
His vitals are stable too.

00:06:30.992 --> 00:06:33.802
There's still hope.

00:06:34.451 --> 00:06:37.054
Just hang in there.

00:06:37.869 --> 00:06:42.219
Professor Min, could you come out for a moment?

00:06:42.219 --> 00:06:43.452
Sure.

00:06:46.125 --> 00:06:48.065
Do you want him prosecuted?

00:06:48.065 --> 00:06:49.703
Was the kidnapping planned?

00:06:49.703 --> 00:06:50.967
Just one comment, please.

00:06:50.967 --> 00:06:53.022
She'll just see Chairman Kang and leave.

00:06:53.022 --> 00:06:54.675
Please step aside.

00:06:55.513 --> 00:06:56.950
How badly are you hurt?

00:06:56.950 --> 00:06:58.239
Is it serious?

00:06:59.897 --> 00:07:03.103
This is a hospital. What are you doing?

00:07:08.451 --> 00:07:13.390
Choiseong will issue a statement soon.

00:07:16.264 --> 00:07:23.230
I apologize again for my family's wrongdoing.

00:07:24.985 --> 00:07:26.731
That's all.

00:07:40.644 --> 00:07:43.408
You should've told the press

00:07:43.408 --> 00:07:50.072
I was at risk of brain damage, needed more tests, and had to be monitored.

00:07:50.693 --> 00:07:52.796
I told you. You're fine.

00:07:52.796 --> 00:07:56.004
I have to sell it to keep Jae Seong locked up.

00:07:56.004 --> 00:07:58.111
Come on.

00:07:58.111 --> 00:08:01.095
Are you really trying to get him arrested?

00:08:01.095 --> 00:08:04.493
Be mad at Kang Jae Seong.

00:08:04.493 --> 00:08:07.338
He kidnapped your wife.

00:08:08.558 --> 00:08:11.751
He committed a crime. He should pay.

00:08:12.712 --> 00:08:18.555
So don't cross me either.

00:08:20.697 --> 00:08:24.437
Your sabbatical's coming up, right?

00:08:24.437 --> 00:08:26.831
Move it up and take Il Jun to the States.

00:08:26.831 --> 00:08:28.524
Why all of a sudden?

00:08:28.524 --> 00:08:30.200
You saw what happened.

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:32.224
Things will only get worse.

00:08:32.224 --> 00:08:34.963
You and Il Jun will get dragged into it.

00:08:34.963 --> 00:08:36.704
Come back when it dies down.

00:08:36.704 --> 00:08:39.096
What about Chairman's treatment?

00:08:39.096 --> 00:08:41.220
Treatment?

00:08:41.220 --> 00:08:44.053
What treatment does he need?

00:08:44.053 --> 00:08:46.623
Well... I mean...

00:08:46.623 --> 00:08:49.370
Secretary Yeo has everything ready.

00:08:49.370 --> 00:08:51.088
Don't worry about Father.

00:08:51.088 --> 00:08:54.844
I've already arranged a new medical team.

00:08:54.844 --> 00:08:57.077
Jae Gyeong...

00:09:00.363 --> 00:09:01.408
Hello?

00:09:01.408 --> 00:09:04.068
How dare you drag my daughter into this?

00:09:04.068 --> 00:09:06.881
Making an enemy of me won't end well for you.

00:09:06.881 --> 00:09:11.841
A little questioning won't tarnish your daughter.

00:09:11.841 --> 00:09:16.579
You should've known where to draw the line.

00:09:16.579 --> 00:09:19.504
<i>Make my daughter CEO of Trading.</i>

00:09:19.504 --> 00:09:23.855
<i>In return, I'll take care of Kang Bang Geul and Kang Jae Seong.</i>

00:09:25.508 --> 00:09:28.321
<i>Sorry, I'm late.</i>

00:09:30.522 --> 00:09:33.268
<i>Looks like it went well.</i>

00:09:39.662 --> 00:09:45.068
<i>I'll handle Choiseong, Jae Seong, and Bang Geul.</i>

00:09:46.552 --> 00:09:50.404
<i>I have plenty on Taeha too.</i>

00:09:58.278 --> 00:10:03.024
Now do you see where Taeha stands?

00:10:14.863 --> 00:10:18.674
Make sure Chairman Kang wakes up.

00:10:18.674 --> 00:10:22.027
We're running out of time to stop Jae Gyeong.

00:10:22.027 --> 00:10:23.258
Got it.

00:10:33.224 --> 00:10:36.108
What did Jae Gyeong promise you to make you do this?

00:10:36.108 --> 00:10:37.494
I'm sorry.

00:10:37.494 --> 00:10:40.652
- I had no choice. - Listen.

00:10:40.652 --> 00:10:44.011
I'm acting chairman now.

00:10:44.011 --> 00:10:47.784
One word from me, and you're fired for falsifying records.

00:10:53.142 --> 00:10:58.056
Restore all the deleted Chemicals slush fund files.

00:10:58.056 --> 00:11:00.169
Use every system we have.

00:11:00.169 --> 00:11:03.751
And recover evidence against Jae Gyeong too.

00:11:03.751 --> 00:11:06.732
- Got it? - Well...

00:11:06.732 --> 00:11:09.021
I may recover some,

00:11:09.021 --> 00:11:12.701
But not everything without the original data.

00:11:21.029 --> 00:11:22.029
[Hwang Jun Hyeon]

00:11:27.953 --> 00:11:32.172
I need the twins' slush fund files from your office safe.

00:11:45.187 --> 00:11:46.187
[Recover Deleted Files]

00:11:48.060 --> 00:11:49.267
[Recovering]

00:11:56.906 --> 00:11:57.941
[System Error: Recovery Stopped]

00:11:59.756 --> 00:12:00.970
What happened?

00:12:00.970 --> 00:12:02.994
The security system caught us.

00:12:02.994 --> 00:12:05.196
What do we do?

00:12:13.424 --> 00:12:17.294
What are you two doing here at this hour?

00:12:17.294 --> 00:12:18.332
Well...

00:12:18.332 --> 00:12:20.155
Tell me.

00:12:20.155 --> 00:12:22.761
Security will protect you.

00:12:25.891 --> 00:12:31.828
He threatened me to plant fake slush fund files.

00:12:31.828 --> 00:12:35.401
When I refused, he said he'd fire me as acting chairman.

00:12:35.401 --> 00:12:36.957
Team Leader Jo!

00:12:38.474 --> 00:12:40.004
Fake files?

00:12:40.004 --> 00:12:41.265
Yes.

00:12:41.265 --> 00:12:44.242
- He gave me these. - Wait, no!

00:12:44.242 --> 00:12:46.242
- No! - Here.

00:12:52.746 --> 00:12:55.491
With Jae Seong gone...

00:12:55.491 --> 00:13:00.668
Did you think Choiseong was yours once I was out of the way?

00:13:01.718 --> 00:13:03.321
Take him to Audit.

00:13:03.321 --> 00:13:04.865
Confiscate his phone.

00:13:04.865 --> 00:13:09.914
No contact with anyone outside Audit without my approval.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:16.129
And naturally, you're no longer acting chairman.

00:13:19.037 --> 00:13:21.722
Jae Gyeong, you can't do this...

00:13:21.722 --> 00:13:23.035
Kang Jae Gyeong!

00:13:23.035 --> 00:13:25.021
Hey, Jae Gyeong!

00:13:42.022 --> 00:13:44.239
Call an emergency meeting.

00:13:44.239 --> 00:13:47.295
Make sure Strategic Planning attends.

00:13:53.744 --> 00:13:59.674
Trading has a slush fund scandal, a cash crisis, and now bankruptcy rumors.

00:14:00.596 --> 00:14:02.737
Yet Director Lee tried

00:14:02.737 --> 00:14:08.004
To fake Chemicals' records just to seize control.

00:14:08.004 --> 00:14:11.441
We can't let this stand.

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:14.754
[Director Lee Sang Jae] He wouldn't do that.

00:14:14.754 --> 00:14:17.342
Could there be some mistake?

00:14:17.342 --> 00:14:23.532
This happened because you all let him play you.

00:14:23.532 --> 00:14:26.556
You kept delaying the succession, and now look at us.

00:14:26.556 --> 00:14:30.414
We gave too much power to a man with no stake here.

00:14:30.414 --> 00:14:33.761
He was never fit to protect this company.

00:14:33.761 --> 00:14:37.001
Why take this public? We could've handled it.

00:14:37.001 --> 00:14:40.774
Can you really say Chemicals is clean?

00:14:40.774 --> 00:14:43.601
Bring me proof.

00:14:43.601 --> 00:14:46.134
Don't just throw accusations around.

00:14:50.135 --> 00:14:55.099
Team Leader Kang, Director Lee trusted you completely.

00:14:55.099 --> 00:14:58.536
As head of Strategic Planning, how will you fix this?

00:14:58.536 --> 00:15:01.307
Do you even have a plan?

00:15:01.307 --> 00:15:04.665
- Well... - You jumped at the promotion.

00:15:04.665 --> 00:15:07.998
Now you're quiet when it counts.

00:15:10.888 --> 00:15:14.507
You must have a better plan, right?

00:15:15.531 --> 00:15:16.982
I do.

00:15:16.982 --> 00:15:20.428
A quick way to stabilize Trading.

00:15:22.254 --> 00:15:27.511
Cut its workforce by 20 percent within a month.

00:15:27.511 --> 00:15:34.020
We'll start with Vice President Choi, who's tied to the slush fund.

00:15:35.314 --> 00:15:37.838
What about Trading's projects?

00:15:37.838 --> 00:15:41.098
The hydrogen project already has government backing.

00:15:41.098 --> 00:15:43.328
"Government backing?"

00:15:43.328 --> 00:15:46.941
The industry minister called this morning.

00:15:46.941 --> 00:15:49.841
They're reconsidering the project.

00:15:51.303 --> 00:15:55.301
Our MOU partners are pulling out.

00:15:55.301 --> 00:16:00.920
Investors want their money back, and banks want their bonds repaid.

00:16:00.920 --> 00:16:05.318
At this rate, the other affiliates will go down too.

00:16:05.318 --> 00:16:09.458
Spinning this without a plan won't solve anything.

00:16:10.458 --> 00:16:14.228
Layoffs will cause a major backlash.

00:16:14.228 --> 00:16:17.075
AI handles much of the work now.

00:16:17.075 --> 00:16:20.732
Cutting excess staff is where the world is headed.

00:16:20.732 --> 00:16:24.582
Are you taking control of Trading's staffing?

00:16:24.582 --> 00:16:26.106
Of course not.

00:16:26.776 --> 00:16:29.309
We already have the right people for that.

00:16:36.352 --> 00:16:40.093
Strategic Planning will handle the layoffs.

00:16:40.093 --> 00:16:44.913
You all saw what they can do on the Yulivia Project.

00:16:44.913 --> 00:16:46.364
We're not HR.

00:16:46.364 --> 00:16:49.043
We can't suddenly handle layoffs.

00:16:49.043 --> 00:16:51.741
You can't just chase flashy wins.

00:16:51.741 --> 00:16:55.341
Do whatever it takes to save the company.

00:16:57.700 --> 00:17:02.479
Handling a crisis is Strategic Planning's job too.

00:17:02.479 --> 00:17:06.532
Not just bragging about landing deals.

00:17:07.637 --> 00:17:09.765
I'll take responsibility too.

00:17:09.765 --> 00:17:12.895
The acting chairman and Trading CEO posts are both vacant.

00:17:14.831 --> 00:17:17.637
So... what do you think?

00:17:24.081 --> 00:17:29.400
Refuse, and your team will be the first to go.

00:17:32.436 --> 00:17:36.089
Should I hand Director Lee over to the prosecutors too?

00:17:40.309 --> 00:17:42.385
See?

00:17:42.385 --> 00:17:44.839
You should've stayed on my side.

00:17:50.402 --> 00:17:53.589
If that's the only way to save the company...

00:17:57.099 --> 00:17:58.519
I'll do it.

00:17:59.552 --> 00:18:02.976
- I'll lead the layoffs. - Hwang Jun Hyeon!

00:18:02.976 --> 00:18:05.095
That's the spirit.

00:18:06.418 --> 00:18:10.950
Make the cuts and save Trading.

00:18:13.437 --> 00:18:15.075
I do hope...

00:18:15.075 --> 00:18:17.161
You succeed.

00:18:33.436 --> 00:18:35.235
Call Strategic Planning.

00:18:35.235 --> 00:18:36.658
Or let me call Mr. Hwang.

00:18:36.658 --> 00:18:41.143
You're not leaving until the investigation is over.

00:18:41.143 --> 00:18:43.357
Are you trying to destroy Choiseong?

00:18:43.357 --> 00:18:45.998
I'm protecting it my way.

00:18:45.998 --> 00:18:50.653
Even if I have to sell off the company or its people.

00:18:50.653 --> 00:18:56.537
When Chairman Kang wakes up, he'll regret how he raised you.

00:19:00.915 --> 00:19:03.599
He'll praise me.

00:19:03.599 --> 00:19:07.303
For doing exactly what he taught me.

00:19:07.303 --> 00:19:08.989
So

00:19:08.989 --> 00:19:14.043
Let me take out the trash,

00:19:14.043 --> 00:19:15.712
Director Lee.

00:19:21.725 --> 00:19:22.998
What about the prosecutors?

00:19:22.998 --> 00:19:26.989
They're digging into his U.S. properties, including a villa in Hawaii.

00:19:26.989 --> 00:19:30.223
They're using it to implicate Na Eun Se.

00:19:30.889 --> 00:19:34.152
Chairman Na should be ready to surrender by now.

00:19:37.032 --> 00:19:39.250
[Chairman Na Byeong Mo]

00:19:39.250 --> 00:19:43.817
What will it take for you to let my daughter go?

00:19:43.817 --> 00:19:46.274
Start with an apology.

00:19:46.274 --> 00:19:49.440
For meddling in Choiseong's affairs.

00:19:51.251 --> 00:19:53.407
I'm sorry.

00:19:53.407 --> 00:19:56.160
I overstepped.

00:19:56.160 --> 00:20:01.239
Hand over your hidden stake in Choiseong Trading.

00:20:01.857 --> 00:20:05.215
Unless you want your precious daughter charged.

00:20:05.215 --> 00:20:07.638
What hidden stake?

00:20:08.978 --> 00:20:12.303
Hard to give up, isn't it?

00:20:12.303 --> 00:20:18.151
But this could spread from your daughter to Taeha.

00:20:18.151 --> 00:20:20.438
Can you handle that?

00:20:32.822 --> 00:20:34.791
[Notice: Choiseong Trading Restructuring]

00:20:34.791 --> 00:20:36.213
[Voluntary Retirement Applications: Strategic Planning]

00:20:52.530 --> 00:20:53.970
Hey.

00:20:55.863 --> 00:20:57.254
How are you?

00:20:57.254 --> 00:21:00.398
I still owe you a meal for my promotion.

00:21:00.398 --> 00:21:03.615
Hello, Team Leader Kang.

00:21:03.615 --> 00:21:05.425
You're busy enough.

00:21:05.425 --> 00:21:07.299
Don't worry about us.

00:21:07.299 --> 00:21:11.819
Please forgive us if we ever upset you.

00:21:11.819 --> 00:21:14.024
We didn't know who you were.

00:21:14.024 --> 00:21:15.949
Huh? Just treat me like before.

00:21:15.949 --> 00:21:18.474
We have work to do.

00:21:18.474 --> 00:21:20.743
- We should go. - We're busy, so...

00:21:25.897 --> 00:21:28.287
Look what you've done.

00:21:28.287 --> 00:21:30.468
Everyone's avoiding us.

00:21:30.468 --> 00:21:33.926
They call it voluntary, but we're forcing people out.

00:21:33.926 --> 00:21:37.314
Yesterday, they were our coworkers. Now we're firing them.

00:21:37.314 --> 00:21:40.004
Go tell her we can't do this.

00:21:40.004 --> 00:21:42.324
This isn't right.

00:21:42.324 --> 00:21:45.095
Jae Gyeong has Director Lee detained.

00:21:46.149 --> 00:21:49.465
She framed him and plans to hand him over.

00:21:49.465 --> 00:21:50.237
What?

00:21:50.237 --> 00:21:54.336
How can we fight her if we all get fired?

00:21:56.414 --> 00:21:59.447
This is for the greater good.

00:22:01.587 --> 00:22:06.158
When a company's struggling, low performers go first.

00:22:06.158 --> 00:22:07.456
Then you do it.

00:22:07.456 --> 00:22:09.882
I could never do it.

00:22:14.169 --> 00:22:16.975
This is impossible.

00:22:24.891 --> 00:22:25.954
<i>You know...</i>

00:22:25.954 --> 00:22:28.287
<i>What could you learn from him?</i>

00:22:29.885 --> 00:22:34.146
You don't still hate me over what happened, do you?

00:22:34.146 --> 00:22:36.171
No. It's not that.

00:22:36.171 --> 00:22:37.463
Sir...

00:22:37.463 --> 00:22:40.311
I was wrong. I'm so sorry.

00:22:40.311 --> 00:22:43.052
My wedding's next month.

00:22:43.052 --> 00:22:44.920
That's great.

00:22:44.920 --> 00:22:49.850
No one wants an unemployed son-in-law.

00:22:49.850 --> 00:22:52.436
I'll do anything.

00:22:52.436 --> 00:22:54.285
Please.

00:22:54.285 --> 00:22:56.932
Just let me get married first.

00:22:56.932 --> 00:22:58.346
[Voluntary Retirement Interviews]

00:22:58.346 --> 00:23:01.512
Manager Kwon Oh Tae, Steel Team 1.

00:23:01.512 --> 00:23:07.484
You know Steel Team 1 came in last, right?

00:23:07.484 --> 00:23:11.770
Could you take one for the team...

00:23:21.471 --> 00:23:24.676
My dad had liver cancer surgery.

00:23:24.676 --> 00:23:28.019
My mom's surgery is next month.

00:23:28.019 --> 00:23:32.665
I've been divorced since last year and am raising two kids.

00:23:33.369 --> 00:23:35.900
I'm so sorry.

00:23:35.900 --> 00:23:39.206
Cut my pay. Just don't fire me.

00:23:40.687 --> 00:23:45.177
You've led Hydrogen well.

00:23:45.177 --> 00:23:46.798
Yeah...

00:23:46.798 --> 00:23:51.811
You're talented, so you'll find another job...

00:23:52.558 --> 00:23:54.370
Hey, don't stop me.

00:23:54.370 --> 00:23:55.682
I'll jump.

00:23:55.682 --> 00:23:57.182
- Come on... - Don't stop me!

00:23:57.182 --> 00:23:59.561
- I'll really jump! - But that's...

00:23:59.561 --> 00:24:01.663
- I mean it! - You can't jump from there.

00:24:01.663 --> 00:24:03.507
- Wait! - Get out of there.

00:24:03.507 --> 00:24:05.854
My leg! I'm stuck!

00:24:05.854 --> 00:24:07.069
- You're stuck? - Yeah.

00:24:07.069 --> 00:24:10.691
- My leg won't budge! Help! - How'd you even get stuck?

00:24:10.691 --> 00:24:12.137
Not one name?

00:24:13.218 --> 00:24:15.828
Everyone has a sob story.

00:24:15.828 --> 00:24:19.726
Just decide if they help the company.

00:24:19.726 --> 00:24:21.992
You heartless bastard. Then you do it!

00:24:21.992 --> 00:24:23.718
Maybe I will.

00:24:24.820 --> 00:24:27.797
This is HR's list, right?

00:24:27.797 --> 00:24:29.670
Fine. You do it!

00:24:31.342 --> 00:24:34.494
Let's see how well you do on your own, you jerks!

00:24:34.494 --> 00:24:37.352
I'll take whatever you offer!

00:24:39.358 --> 00:24:41.043
This is such bullshit!

00:24:45.354 --> 00:24:49.132
Is that job offer still open?

00:24:49.132 --> 00:24:52.012
I can start this week.

00:25:02.859 --> 00:25:05.038
You can't come in.

00:25:09.429 --> 00:25:12.763
Cutting 20 percent in a month won't be easy, huh?

00:25:12.763 --> 00:25:18.522
Would you wreck Trading just to own it?

00:25:18.522 --> 00:25:23.830
Your mother wore that same innocent look when she took over our home.

00:25:23.830 --> 00:25:27.347
- You came back for the rest, too. - Don't push me.

00:25:27.347 --> 00:25:29.853
You're making me want to.

00:25:30.540 --> 00:25:32.365
Like you could.

00:25:33.589 --> 00:25:35.741
Don't get cocky.

00:25:35.741 --> 00:25:38.019
You're next after Jae Seong.

00:25:38.019 --> 00:25:40.479
You want to save Trading?

00:25:40.479 --> 00:25:46.747
Give me Smile Investment's 30 percent stake in Choiseong Solutions.

00:25:47.970 --> 00:25:48.999
What?

00:25:48.999 --> 00:25:52.326
Or cut the staff yourself.

00:25:52.326 --> 00:25:55.206
Drop the good-girl act.

00:26:00.130 --> 00:26:02.969
Mr. Hwang Ji Hun, Sales Team 3.

00:26:04.069 --> 00:26:07.962
About your performance review...

00:26:12.668 --> 00:26:14.796
Is this really right?

00:26:14.796 --> 00:26:20.787
These people worked hard for this company.

00:26:22.943 --> 00:26:30.981
Some swore they'd give their all, then coasted on a paycheck.

00:26:30.981 --> 00:26:32.497
You know?

00:26:32.497 --> 00:26:35.461
You're the chairman's daughter.

00:26:35.461 --> 00:26:37.134
Why side with them?

00:26:37.134 --> 00:26:39.502
It's your father's money!

00:26:39.502 --> 00:26:41.623
Because I feel guilty!

00:26:41.623 --> 00:26:42.339
What?

00:26:42.339 --> 00:26:45.456
My siblings caused the hit-and-run and disgraced the company.

00:26:45.456 --> 00:26:47.360
Why should the employees pay?

00:26:47.360 --> 00:26:48.686
They gave it their all.

00:26:48.686 --> 00:26:54.350
They write proposals, work on-site, and bust their butts.

00:26:54.350 --> 00:26:56.777
You can't expect them to work like owners.

00:26:56.777 --> 00:26:59.219
Pay them like owners, then.

00:26:59.219 --> 00:27:01.243
- Are you done? - No.

00:27:01.243 --> 00:27:03.073
Be honest.

00:27:03.073 --> 00:27:07.003
Haeseong Port, GF Solutions, and the Yulivia lithium deal...

00:27:07.003 --> 00:27:09.167
You got rich, so you don't care.

00:27:09.167 --> 00:27:11.464
Employees land deals too.

00:27:11.464 --> 00:27:13.489
But they get scraps.

00:27:13.489 --> 00:27:15.620
At least we should be on their side.

00:27:15.620 --> 00:27:18.369
Why do Jae Gyeong's dirty work?

00:27:18.369 --> 00:27:20.369
What else can we do?

00:27:21.514 --> 00:27:24.028
Let them take Director Lee?

00:27:24.028 --> 00:27:27.081
Or let Jae Gyeong cut us down herself?

00:27:27.081 --> 00:27:29.225
I'm out of options!

00:27:29.225 --> 00:27:31.545
We have one!

00:27:31.545 --> 00:27:36.038
Sell the 30 percent stake in Choiseong Solutions.

00:27:37.709 --> 00:27:39.802
That'll cover Trading's cash crunch.

00:27:39.802 --> 00:27:43.073
That money came from Trading anyway.

00:27:44.152 --> 00:27:46.363
That won't stop her.

00:27:46.363 --> 00:27:48.669
Look what she did to your brother.

00:27:48.669 --> 00:27:50.423
Who said I'd give it to her?

00:27:50.423 --> 00:27:53.463
She'll end up with it.

00:27:53.463 --> 00:27:55.169
Wait...

00:27:55.884 --> 00:27:58.743
- You care that much about it? - Yeah.

00:28:00.151 --> 00:28:02.048
I do.

00:28:02.048 --> 00:28:04.581
Choiseong Solutions needs years to pay off.

00:28:04.581 --> 00:28:08.085
Our stake could skyrocket. We can't just give it up.

00:28:08.085 --> 00:28:10.085
Who would that help?

00:28:12.942 --> 00:28:17.446
We fought for that stake to protect Choiseong.

00:28:17.446 --> 00:28:19.709
I'm not giving it up.

00:28:19.709 --> 00:28:22.643
And I won't do what she wants.

00:28:22.643 --> 00:28:27.216
How are you any different from her?

00:28:29.373 --> 00:28:30.870
Do what you want.

00:28:30.870 --> 00:28:32.816
So will I.

00:28:34.506 --> 00:28:36.388
Watch your mouth!

00:28:36.388 --> 00:28:39.075
You think this is easy for me?

00:28:44.797 --> 00:28:45.869
Yeah.

00:28:45.869 --> 00:28:48.543
It's all my fault.

00:28:48.543 --> 00:28:51.212
My son's behind bars because of me.

00:28:51.212 --> 00:28:54.193
My eldest only cares about herself.

00:28:54.193 --> 00:28:55.357
And my youngest...

00:28:55.357 --> 00:28:58.030
<i>How are you any different from her?</i>

00:28:58.030 --> 00:29:01.328
Mouths off to her own father.

00:29:01.328 --> 00:29:05.456
What a great family I raised.

00:29:09.732 --> 00:29:11.102
Manager Lee Dong Ho?

00:29:11.102 --> 00:29:13.462
Yes, this is Lee Dong Ho.

00:29:13.462 --> 00:29:16.959
Why would I meet you?

00:29:16.959 --> 00:29:18.559
I'm not going.

00:29:18.559 --> 00:29:20.559
I said no.

00:29:24.799 --> 00:29:26.747
[Voluntary Retirement Application]

00:29:30.634 --> 00:29:33.658
Why is he so eager to fire everyone?

00:29:33.658 --> 00:29:35.251
Has money gone to his head?

00:29:35.251 --> 00:29:38.058
All he cares about is lining his pockets.

00:29:38.825 --> 00:29:40.668
Slow down.

00:29:40.668 --> 00:29:43.488
He's probably frustrated too.

00:29:43.488 --> 00:29:46.232
He just wants to save Trading.

00:29:46.232 --> 00:29:49.986
A company shouldn't treat its people like this.

00:29:49.986 --> 00:29:55.033
Who can spend years fighting an unfair dismissal?

00:29:55.033 --> 00:29:57.226
They have families to support.

00:29:57.226 --> 00:30:00.306
Lose one paycheck, and the bills pile up.

00:30:00.306 --> 00:30:02.930
He has family too. His grandma depends on him.

00:30:02.930 --> 00:30:07.271
He's just putting on a show for the higher-ups.

00:30:07.271 --> 00:30:08.897
Don't worry too much.

00:30:08.897 --> 00:30:11.983
Have some meat with your drink.

00:30:11.983 --> 00:30:14.736
[Pork Skirt, Pork Jowl, Hwangjesal] "Hwang"-jesal?

00:30:16.171 --> 00:30:18.843
Did you order this?

00:30:18.843 --> 00:30:22.393
I can't even stand the name "Hwang!"

00:30:22.393 --> 00:30:26.819
Pretend it's Hwang Jun Hyeon and chew him to pieces.

00:30:27.783 --> 00:30:31.088
Then I'll burn him to a crisp!

00:30:35.157 --> 00:30:36.994
[Performance Reviews]

00:30:38.023 --> 00:30:39.133
[Voluntary Retirement Candidates]

00:30:56.466 --> 00:31:00.079
Jae Gyeong, what are you up to?

00:31:01.766 --> 00:31:05.153
You didn't give Jae Gyeong your hidden stake, right?

00:31:06.174 --> 00:31:08.456
What a pity.

00:31:08.456 --> 00:31:10.720
You've lost so much weight.

00:31:10.720 --> 00:31:12.655
You've been through a lot.

00:31:12.655 --> 00:31:14.679
What are you doing here?

00:31:14.679 --> 00:31:16.703
I'm not that heartless.

00:31:16.703 --> 00:31:19.280
I got you out, didn't I?

00:31:19.280 --> 00:31:21.836
You know I mean well. Right?

00:31:22.474 --> 00:31:23.924
Have a seat.

00:31:23.924 --> 00:31:25.791
She has an offer.

00:31:25.791 --> 00:31:29.471
She tried to take me down with my husband!

00:31:29.471 --> 00:31:32.231
How can you even listen to her?

00:31:34.204 --> 00:31:36.675
You sure you won't regret that?

00:31:36.675 --> 00:31:39.657
You don't even know what I'm offering.

00:32:01.871 --> 00:32:03.148
What?

00:32:03.148 --> 00:32:05.001
What are they plotting?

00:32:05.001 --> 00:32:07.408
Don't be so mad.

00:32:07.408 --> 00:32:10.075
You should be thanking me.

00:32:10.075 --> 00:32:12.671
Don't go back on your word.

00:32:13.477 --> 00:32:16.030
I said I'd give it to you.

00:32:19.694 --> 00:32:20.697
[Manager Park Bong Gi]

00:32:23.603 --> 00:32:25.058
Sir...

00:32:25.717 --> 00:32:30.210
What could my sister possibly offer Na Eun Se?

00:32:36.663 --> 00:32:39.216
Thought you never wanted to see me again.

00:32:41.677 --> 00:32:44.467
Why'd you bring her?

00:32:44.467 --> 00:32:46.607
How'd you know I was here?

00:32:47.233 --> 00:32:50.531
See? He's not even happy. Why'd we come?

00:32:50.531 --> 00:32:53.395
Did you forget our Yulivia dream team?

00:32:53.395 --> 00:32:56.359
Why are you fighting each other?

00:32:56.359 --> 00:32:59.209
Come on. Make up.

00:32:59.209 --> 00:33:01.547
Play nice.

00:33:01.547 --> 00:33:02.779
Play nice.

00:33:02.779 --> 00:33:05.176
We've got tons to do.

00:33:05.176 --> 00:33:08.393
Jun Hyeon, come eat! I made ribs!

00:33:08.393 --> 00:33:10.016
Let's go.

00:33:10.016 --> 00:33:12.351
- We have work. - Grandma!

00:33:12.351 --> 00:33:14.483
I'm coming!

00:33:14.483 --> 00:33:15.922
- Wait.. - Give me plenty.

00:33:26.408 --> 00:33:28.501
Eat up.

00:33:30.941 --> 00:33:33.545
You said she had dementia.

00:33:33.545 --> 00:33:38.139
I think she's faking it just to mess with me.

00:33:38.139 --> 00:33:40.306
Knock it off.

00:33:40.306 --> 00:33:43.832
Hey! Why'd you hit my boy?

00:33:47.336 --> 00:33:51.580
That hit-and-run scumbag is Chairman Kang Yong Ho, huh?

00:33:51.580 --> 00:33:54.880
If he wakes up, I'll knock him back out.

00:33:55.950 --> 00:33:58.388
Why say something so scary?

00:33:58.388 --> 00:34:00.748
Now I can't eat.

00:34:00.748 --> 00:34:03.548
- That's not what I... - Enough.

00:34:03.548 --> 00:34:05.356
You're making this awkward.

00:34:05.356 --> 00:34:10.254
Grandma, this is for you. I bought it earlier.

00:34:10.254 --> 00:34:15.872
Your grandson can see where you are, so you'll always feel close.

00:34:18.448 --> 00:34:21.553
- It's a gift. - Well, look at that.

00:34:21.553 --> 00:34:23.333
Sorry I hit you.

00:34:26.053 --> 00:34:28.680
Situational awareness.

00:34:28.680 --> 00:34:30.903
Always watch your surroundings.

00:34:30.903 --> 00:34:34.225
That's how you spot an attack coming.

00:34:34.225 --> 00:34:36.158
Defense 101.

00:34:38.413 --> 00:34:40.864
You eat up too.

00:34:40.864 --> 00:34:42.387
Okay.

00:34:42.387 --> 00:34:44.174
Why are you here?

00:34:44.174 --> 00:34:46.570
Anyone wants you here.

00:34:59.352 --> 00:35:04.422
Look what I'm doing for my own son.

00:35:04.422 --> 00:35:06.787
Don't act like I asked.

00:35:06.787 --> 00:35:08.964
Then I'll take it back.

00:35:08.964 --> 00:35:10.534
Come on.

00:35:10.534 --> 00:35:12.520
Why are you really here?

00:35:13.314 --> 00:35:16.294
What do you want from me?

00:35:19.695 --> 00:35:21.618
You're scared, huh?

00:35:22.902 --> 00:35:25.287
Scared Jae Gyeong will take everything.

00:35:25.287 --> 00:35:27.156
Watch your mouth.

00:35:27.156 --> 00:35:30.084
I'm the eldest son of Choiseong.

00:35:30.084 --> 00:35:33.221
- Kang Jae Seong. - I know.

00:35:33.221 --> 00:35:35.811
Then act like it.

00:35:35.811 --> 00:35:37.835
Don't let her beat you.

00:35:37.835 --> 00:35:40.109
You're about to lose Trading too.

00:35:40.109 --> 00:35:43.588
And all you can do is act tough with me.

00:35:43.588 --> 00:35:47.524
- Hey! - How long will you stay angry?

00:35:48.643 --> 00:35:51.961
Stop feeling sorry for yourself.

00:35:51.961 --> 00:35:57.804
Think about what you can do and who you can join forces with.

00:36:02.019 --> 00:36:04.824
One thing is clear.

00:36:04.824 --> 00:36:07.530
Jae Gyeong is your enemy.

00:36:10.367 --> 00:36:13.077
So eat.

00:36:13.077 --> 00:36:16.931
You need a full stomach to think straight.

00:36:16.931 --> 00:36:19.064
I have a plan too.

00:36:19.064 --> 00:36:22.164
You think I'll be in here forever?

00:36:24.106 --> 00:36:27.725
Don't underestimate me just because I'm locked up.

00:36:36.252 --> 00:36:38.716
Vice President Choi is still under investigation.

00:36:38.716 --> 00:36:40.710
But Eun Se got released.

00:36:40.710 --> 00:36:42.040
Right.

00:36:42.040 --> 00:36:45.036
At first, she wanted them all gone.

00:36:45.036 --> 00:36:47.428
This is HR's list.

00:36:47.428 --> 00:36:50.406
Looks like they're purging Jae Seong's people.

00:36:50.406 --> 00:36:52.695
But there's more to it.

00:36:52.695 --> 00:36:54.048
The Hydrogen Division?

00:36:54.048 --> 00:36:56.395
So is Mr. Yoon from R&D.

00:36:56.395 --> 00:36:59.075
Production, Mobility, Global Cooperation...

00:36:59.075 --> 00:37:01.754
Key people are all over this list.

00:37:01.754 --> 00:37:03.824
Manager Lee is the main target.

00:37:03.824 --> 00:37:07.624
I knew his review looked strange.

00:37:07.624 --> 00:37:11.174
If anyone stays, it has to be him.

00:37:11.174 --> 00:37:13.634
He's Chairman Kang's top pick.

00:37:14.643 --> 00:37:17.323
What the hell is going on?

00:37:20.313 --> 00:37:22.337
You lying bastards!

00:37:22.337 --> 00:37:23.879
What?

00:37:25.157 --> 00:37:28.287
Only 30 million won in severance?

00:37:28.287 --> 00:37:32.009
You think I worked here for 15 years for this?

00:37:32.009 --> 00:37:34.162
Who told you that?

00:37:34.162 --> 00:37:36.013
They promised two years' salary.

00:37:36.013 --> 00:37:38.156
I checked with General Affairs.

00:37:38.156 --> 00:37:40.349
How could you deceive me?

00:37:40.349 --> 00:37:43.295
Do you know how hard this was to sign?

00:37:45.089 --> 00:37:46.352
Jae Gyeong did this.

00:37:46.352 --> 00:37:50.102
Fifteen years meant nothing?

00:37:50.102 --> 00:37:51.959
What a dirty trick.

00:37:51.959 --> 00:37:54.992
You put half my team on the list too.

00:37:54.992 --> 00:37:56.934
Please calm down, sir.

00:37:56.934 --> 00:37:58.763
Fine.

00:37:58.763 --> 00:38:01.142
Maybe I'm a lousy manager.

00:38:01.142 --> 00:38:05.943
But my team is the best in the business.

00:38:06.701 --> 00:38:09.559
You'll regret this.

00:38:09.559 --> 00:38:13.839
Chairman Kang never treated his people like this.

00:38:14.889 --> 00:38:17.949
What happened to Choiseong?

00:38:20.697 --> 00:38:23.517
- Manager Lee! - Sir!

00:38:29.603 --> 00:38:32.902
Are you really letting him walk away?

00:38:34.992 --> 00:38:36.954
<i>Situational awareness.</i>

00:38:36.954 --> 00:38:38.978
<i>Always watch your surroundings.</i>

00:38:38.978 --> 00:38:43.040
<i>That's how you spot an attack coming.</i>

00:38:43.040 --> 00:38:44.308
<i>Defense 101.</i>

00:38:44.995 --> 00:38:46.933
Not a chance.

00:38:46.933 --> 00:38:50.538
Manager Park, let's ask them for help.

00:39:00.470 --> 00:39:02.060
Things are awful now.

00:39:02.060 --> 00:39:04.600
I heard the whole Hydrogen team is quitting.

00:39:04.600 --> 00:39:06.405
Must be chaos over there.

00:39:06.405 --> 00:39:08.628
They seemed happy.

00:39:08.628 --> 00:39:12.548
- Maybe they found better jobs. - Or they've just lost it.

00:39:12.548 --> 00:39:14.070
"Better jobs?"

00:39:14.070 --> 00:39:17.145
I heard headhunters are camped out in the lobby.

00:39:17.145 --> 00:39:18.179
Yeah.

00:39:18.179 --> 00:39:19.524
Anyone get an offer?

00:39:19.524 --> 00:39:22.331
They're only meeting with the Hydrogen team.

00:39:23.754 --> 00:39:27.524
The cafe behind the office is where it's happening.

00:39:27.524 --> 00:39:29.310
<i>The cafe behind the office.</i>

00:39:31.999 --> 00:39:35.855
Come on, it's just a meeting.

00:39:35.855 --> 00:39:37.660
Just say hello.

00:39:37.660 --> 00:39:39.427
But...

00:39:40.299 --> 00:39:42.364
Oh, hello.

00:39:42.364 --> 00:39:43.925
Please.

00:39:45.079 --> 00:39:46.456
Nice to meet you.

00:39:46.456 --> 00:39:49.902
This is Manager Lee Dong Ho from the Hydrogen team.

00:39:52.730 --> 00:39:54.754
I heard you met with Manager Lee.

00:39:54.754 --> 00:39:58.231
He hasn't agreed yet. MD Kwon is pressuring him.

00:39:58.231 --> 00:40:00.691
He cares a lot about his team.

00:40:00.691 --> 00:40:01.996
He'll cave in soon.

00:40:01.996 --> 00:40:04.538
Just honor our deal.

00:40:05.352 --> 00:40:07.809
Don't worry.

00:40:07.809 --> 00:40:10.115
I told you.

00:40:48.596 --> 00:40:50.767
I'll handle this. Manager Park?

00:40:50.767 --> 00:40:54.807
I'll check every tip, text, photo, and recording.

00:40:54.807 --> 00:40:56.807
And Bang Geul...

00:40:58.854 --> 00:41:01.253
Let's finish this tonight.

00:41:48.116 --> 00:41:51.750
[Hydrogen Business Divestment Plan] So this is why she pushed the layoffs.

00:41:54.291 --> 00:41:57.907
The man Manager Lee met works for Taeha Energy.

00:41:57.907 --> 00:42:01.571
Looks like Taeha plans to poach the whole Hydrogen team.

00:42:01.571 --> 00:42:03.975
Can they take the whole team?

00:42:03.975 --> 00:42:06.708
They're close-knit.

00:42:06.708 --> 00:42:09.185
They all look up to Manager Lee.

00:42:09.185 --> 00:42:11.209
Relationships matter at work.

00:42:11.209 --> 00:42:14.133
You can't blame them.

00:42:14.133 --> 00:42:18.226
The rest will leave together before the team falls apart.

00:42:18.226 --> 00:42:21.979
She used us as cover, then told Taeha when to make its move.

00:42:24.874 --> 00:42:26.800
Let's win Manager Lee back first.

00:42:32.232 --> 00:42:34.179
Let's take the other one.

00:42:40.781 --> 00:42:42.408
[Hydrogen Team]

00:42:58.161 --> 00:43:00.934
<i>Choiseong Trading was nearing debt restructuring,</i>

00:43:00.934 --> 00:43:02.958
<i>but can now breathe again.</i>

00:43:02.958 --> 00:43:05.815
<i>It secured 300 billion won by selling</i>

00:43:05.815 --> 00:43:08.459
<i>its hydrogen business to Taeha Energy.</i>

00:43:08.459 --> 00:43:10.259
<i>This marks a fresh start.</i>

00:43:10.259 --> 00:43:14.914
<i>Analysts say CEO Kang, who led the deal,</i>

00:43:14.914 --> 00:43:19.415
<i>has all but secured her place as Choiseong's successor.</i>

00:43:19.415 --> 00:43:25.419
<i>All eyes are now on Choiseong's next move.</i>

00:43:25.419 --> 00:43:28.798
Your father won't be happy when he finds out.

00:43:28.798 --> 00:43:31.804
Feelings have no place in business.

00:43:33.648 --> 00:43:36.991
<i>You want me to hand the hydrogen business to Trading?</i>

00:43:36.991 --> 00:43:39.459
<i>I spent three years building it.</i>

00:43:39.459 --> 00:43:42.866
<i>We're working with the government on renewable hydrogen.</i>

00:43:42.866 --> 00:43:46.584
<i>We've even finished talks on using nuclear power to produce it.</i>

00:43:46.584 --> 00:43:49.000
<i>Why does Jae Seong get to take it?</i>

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:51.393
<i>You think you got this far on your own?</i>

00:43:51.393 --> 00:43:53.259
<i>Kang Jae Gyeong.</i>

00:43:54.057 --> 00:43:57.087
<i>They shook hands with me.</i>

00:43:57.087 --> 00:44:01.186
<i>They want to work with the Choiseong I built.</i>

00:44:01.186 --> 00:44:03.093
<i>Not with you.</i>

00:44:03.093 --> 00:44:07.439
<i>Starting today, Trading controls the hydrogen business.</i>

00:44:07.439 --> 00:44:09.632
<i>I'm in charge.</i>

00:44:09.632 --> 00:44:11.997
<i>It's for the group.</i>

00:44:11.997 --> 00:44:13.984
<i>So...</i>

00:44:13.984 --> 00:44:16.477
<i>Hand it over intact.</i>

00:44:21.549 --> 00:44:23.884
[Supplemental Investment Agreement] Just as promised.

00:44:23.884 --> 00:44:26.850
Three hundred billion for the sale, plus a hundred off the books.

00:44:26.850 --> 00:44:31.566
You can pocket it without a trace.

00:44:31.566 --> 00:44:34.076
Secretary Jo will launder it clean.

00:44:34.076 --> 00:44:36.229
One percent of the hydrogen profits...

00:44:36.229 --> 00:44:38.955
And your hidden stake in Trading.

00:44:45.033 --> 00:44:47.933
You really know how to make a deal.

00:44:48.852 --> 00:44:53.139
I'll hand over the tech team once the balance is paid.

00:44:53.139 --> 00:44:55.257
The sooner, the better.

00:44:55.257 --> 00:44:57.499
- Right? - Yeah.

00:44:57.499 --> 00:44:59.056
Of course.

00:45:06.757 --> 00:45:12.208
Not even a "thank-you" after cleaning me out.

00:45:12.208 --> 00:45:16.161
Let's see if she has her father's patience.

00:45:24.980 --> 00:45:27.146
The executives are waiting.

00:45:42.273 --> 00:45:44.556
I was just about to call you.

00:45:44.556 --> 00:45:48.769
Thanks to you, the sale went through without a fight.

00:45:49.464 --> 00:45:51.250
How can I repay you?

00:45:51.250 --> 00:45:52.681
Was this your plan?

00:45:52.681 --> 00:45:55.950
Distract everyone with layoffs, then make a deal with Taeha?

00:45:55.950 --> 00:45:58.829
Why sell the hydrogen business?

00:46:00.455 --> 00:46:03.299
Because Father built it

00:46:03.299 --> 00:46:05.719
For Jae Seong.

00:46:07.521 --> 00:46:09.968
He was always like that.

00:46:09.968 --> 00:46:14.444
He gave Jae Seong the best of everything.

00:46:15.216 --> 00:46:19.376
So I learned to fight alone.

00:46:19.376 --> 00:46:20.789
Once,

00:46:21.483 --> 00:46:24.849
I cut the strings on a harp Father bought him.

00:46:36.959 --> 00:46:40.205
I expected hell. But...

00:46:44.876 --> 00:46:46.989
He said nothing.

00:46:48.258 --> 00:46:50.211
That's when I learned.

00:46:52.551 --> 00:46:55.644
All I had to do was win.

00:46:56.291 --> 00:46:59.384
Then he'd let anything slide.

00:47:01.115 --> 00:47:02.797
<i>Back then...</i>

00:47:02.797 --> 00:47:05.715
<i>I thought looking away was best.</i>

00:47:06.468 --> 00:47:09.768
<i>I didn't want to hurt you more...</i>

00:47:11.211 --> 00:47:13.235
<i>It was me.</i>

00:47:13.235 --> 00:47:16.541
<i>I turned you into a monster.</i>

00:47:18.878 --> 00:47:21.236
I'll look the other way too.

00:47:21.236 --> 00:47:23.276
Come back to me.

00:47:24.741 --> 00:47:26.865
As you can see,

00:47:26.865 --> 00:47:29.374
Choiseong is mine now.

00:48:06.166 --> 00:48:11.239
<i>You think my Choiseong falls that easy?</i>

00:48:15.356 --> 00:48:18.162
So I'm the one...

00:48:25.411 --> 00:48:28.257
Who brought Choiseong down.

00:48:46.146 --> 00:48:48.999
<i>I think I found Director Lee.</i>

00:48:55.362 --> 00:48:57.514
What's taking her so long?

00:49:00.981 --> 00:49:03.832
- You're sure it's Director Lee? - I'm telling you.

00:49:03.832 --> 00:49:05.605
I was shocked.

00:49:20.935 --> 00:49:22.246
Ma'am.

00:49:22.246 --> 00:49:24.512
Can we borrow this one?

00:50:07.907 --> 00:50:10.324
Sorry. One second!

00:50:10.324 --> 00:50:12.495
Oh, dear. Hold still.

00:50:12.495 --> 00:50:13.574
I'll clean you up.

00:50:13.574 --> 00:50:16.167
Director Lee, this way!

00:50:22.787 --> 00:50:24.858
What the hell are you doing?

00:50:24.858 --> 00:50:27.344
- Stop that! - Sorry!

00:50:30.821 --> 00:50:32.514
Hey!

00:50:52.278 --> 00:50:54.274
I'm fine.

00:50:54.274 --> 00:50:57.180
I got locked up and broke out.

00:50:58.225 --> 00:51:00.044
Kind of fun.

00:51:01.831 --> 00:51:03.768
There's a way to save Trading.

00:51:03.768 --> 00:51:06.329
It's too late to sell the Smile stake.

00:51:06.329 --> 00:51:08.353
Chairman Na won't give back the hydrogen business.

00:51:08.353 --> 00:51:11.676
If Jae Gyeong becomes chairman, it's over.

00:51:11.676 --> 00:51:14.728
Trading may be a shell now, but we have to save it.

00:51:14.728 --> 00:51:16.184
What can we do?

00:51:16.184 --> 00:51:18.355
Get Jae Seong out.

00:51:18.355 --> 00:51:22.955
Pin Trading's slush fund on Chairman Kang.

00:51:25.831 --> 00:51:29.738
Jae Seong's shares can save Trading.

00:51:29.738 --> 00:51:32.402
We can take back Hydrogen and...

00:51:32.402 --> 00:51:35.548
You'd make him a criminal again?

00:51:36.302 --> 00:51:37.992
Are you serious?

00:51:37.992 --> 00:51:41.672
Even Director Lee thinks you've lost it.

00:51:41.672 --> 00:51:42.977
Bang Geul's right here.

00:51:42.977 --> 00:51:44.696
Show some respect.

00:51:44.696 --> 00:51:48.643
Even if Chairman Kang wakes up, he can't return to work.

00:51:48.643 --> 00:51:50.722
This is our best option.

00:51:53.274 --> 00:51:55.705
What about his honor?

00:51:55.705 --> 00:51:57.241
What about his whole life?

00:51:57.241 --> 00:51:59.641
Does that matter right now?

00:52:00.408 --> 00:52:02.278
Be realistic.

00:52:02.278 --> 00:52:05.054
One man has to take the fall.

00:52:06.062 --> 00:52:08.567
Who are you to decide that?

00:52:08.567 --> 00:52:10.872
I can take responsibility.

00:52:10.872 --> 00:52:12.952
I'll fix this somehow.

00:52:12.952 --> 00:52:14.301
How dare...

00:52:15.754 --> 00:52:16.805
Are you okay?

00:52:16.805 --> 00:52:19.098
You think my dad's a pushover?

00:52:19.793 --> 00:52:24.012
My dad isn't someone you can just throw away!

00:52:24.012 --> 00:52:27.706
Who are you to ruin his life?

00:52:27.706 --> 00:52:29.731
He's Kang Yong Ho!

00:52:29.731 --> 00:52:32.344
Chairman of Choiseong Group!

00:52:34.871 --> 00:52:37.618
I thought you hated me.

00:52:37.618 --> 00:52:38.881
You're laughing?

00:52:41.189 --> 00:52:43.120
Want another one?

00:52:43.120 --> 00:52:46.937
You can beat me to death. My answer won't change.

00:52:46.937 --> 00:52:50.163
Chairman Kang has to take the fall.

00:52:51.070 --> 00:52:54.836
Just this once... sell out your father.

00:53:04.206 --> 00:53:06.662
I should've hit him harder.

00:53:06.662 --> 00:53:09.172
Dad's the one who'll be branded a criminal.

00:53:09.172 --> 00:53:12.254
Who is he to say it's okay?

00:53:12.254 --> 00:53:14.047
He's not wrong.

00:53:14.047 --> 00:53:15.082
Mom!

00:53:15.082 --> 00:53:18.645
Your father would say the same.

00:53:18.645 --> 00:53:22.964
It would protect his children too.

00:53:24.400 --> 00:53:29.539
He never showed it, but you kids meant everything to him.

00:53:30.330 --> 00:53:32.953
I don't want that.

00:53:32.953 --> 00:53:36.717
Everyone will point fingers and curse him.

00:53:36.717 --> 00:53:38.645
Don't you feel sorry for him?

00:53:38.645 --> 00:53:44.705
Before he's your Dad, or my husband, he's Chairman of Choiseong.

00:53:44.705 --> 00:53:49.238
If sacrificing himself could save the company, he'd do it.

00:53:50.289 --> 00:53:54.682
That's how your father lived.

00:54:01.114 --> 00:54:04.585
You helped Director Lee escape, right?

00:54:04.585 --> 00:54:07.451
You locked up an innocent man.

00:54:08.325 --> 00:54:12.438
We'll see how innocent he is.

00:54:15.209 --> 00:54:17.890
Don't touch Director Lee!

00:54:25.785 --> 00:54:27.555
[Hwang Jun Hyeon] <i>It's your choice.</i>

00:54:27.555 --> 00:54:30.991
<i>You're the only one who can save Choiseong.</i>

00:54:39.002 --> 00:54:41.552
It's all thanks to you.

00:54:41.552 --> 00:54:43.401
It was a hard decision,

00:54:43.401 --> 00:54:49.766
But selling the hydrogen business was the only way to save Trading.

00:54:49.766 --> 00:54:52.419
Na Eun Se was a big help too.

00:54:59.205 --> 00:55:01.647
People still aren't convinced.

00:55:01.647 --> 00:55:05.061
Perhaps we should let her go.

00:55:05.061 --> 00:55:11.905
Give her a chance to make up for her husband's mistakes.

00:55:12.511 --> 00:55:14.496
For my sake.

00:55:14.496 --> 00:55:16.244
Got it.

00:55:21.074 --> 00:55:22.964
Thank you.

00:55:22.964 --> 00:55:24.964
CEO Kang.

00:55:31.665 --> 00:55:33.882
Good to see you all.

00:55:33.882 --> 00:55:37.895
Kang Jae Seong is back from the dead.

00:55:39.296 --> 00:55:43.528
You... How did you get out?

00:55:55.701 --> 00:56:02.744
Chairman Kang Yong Ho ordered the 300 billion won slush fund...

00:56:04.143 --> 00:56:05.938
To be set up under Jae Seong's name.

00:56:05.938 --> 00:56:08.715
I've submitted the evidence to the prosecutors.

00:56:08.715 --> 00:56:11.241
I'll testify to everything.

00:56:11.241 --> 00:56:14.709
I apologize for causing public concern.

00:56:15.990 --> 00:56:20.730
<i>CEO Kang Jae Seong's role in the slush fund scandal</i>

00:56:20.730 --> 00:56:24.590
<i>may now be reviewed from scratch.</i>

00:56:26.953 --> 00:56:30.170
He will be released pending investigation.

00:56:30.170 --> 00:56:33.423
The prosecutors will question him as a witness.

00:56:36.705 --> 00:56:40.181
<i>You want me to sell out Father?</i>

00:56:40.181 --> 00:56:43.530
<i>You're really trying to make me total scum?</i>

00:56:43.530 --> 00:56:46.453
<i>Did you plan this with your mom to piss me off?</i>

00:56:46.453 --> 00:56:49.277
<i>Then rot in here forever.</i>

00:56:49.277 --> 00:56:53.767
<i>You framed Dad for the hit-and-run, and hid a slush fund.</i>

00:56:53.767 --> 00:56:55.505
<i>Serve your time.</i>

00:56:56.416 --> 00:56:57.880
<i>Wait.</i>

00:56:57.880 --> 00:56:59.804
<i>Why the rush?</i>

00:56:59.804 --> 00:57:02.180
<i>That's not what I meant.</i>

00:57:03.224 --> 00:57:05.331
<i>Don't get the wrong idea.</i>

00:57:05.331 --> 00:57:11.188
<i>I'm betraying Dad to save Choiseong, not to save you.</i>

00:57:12.685 --> 00:57:18.827
<i>I won't let Jae Gyeong take the company he devoted his life to.</i>

00:57:21.710 --> 00:57:23.503
<i>Yeah.</i>

00:57:25.249 --> 00:57:27.495
<i>That evil witch.</i>

00:57:29.417 --> 00:57:34.694
<i>From now on, you do exactly as I say.</i>

00:57:34.694 --> 00:57:36.057
<i>Yeah.</i>

00:57:36.057 --> 00:57:39.174
<i>I'm your loyal lackey now.</i>

00:57:40.509 --> 00:57:43.569
<i>At your service!</i>

00:57:48.929 --> 00:57:52.086
You looked after Trading while I was gone?

00:57:52.086 --> 00:57:53.960
Good job.

00:57:53.960 --> 00:57:58.950
The slush fund case will be dropped for lack of evidence.

00:57:58.950 --> 00:58:03.850
And the kidnapping? We just went for a drive.

00:58:03.850 --> 00:58:07.950
The price of being famous, I guess.

00:58:10.073 --> 00:58:13.270
You won't press charges now, huh?

00:58:13.270 --> 00:58:18.155
You care too much about Choiseong for that.

00:58:18.155 --> 00:58:19.721
Right?

00:58:24.556 --> 00:58:28.046
I'm sorry I worried you all.

00:58:28.046 --> 00:58:30.167
Prison knocked some sense into me.

00:58:30.167 --> 00:58:35.569
I'll behave and work hard from now on.

00:58:35.569 --> 00:58:38.443
Let's go, guys!

00:58:44.596 --> 00:58:49.503
I'm so sick of this fight.

00:58:54.307 --> 00:58:57.279
Let's drink! Cheers!

00:59:00.276 --> 00:59:02.300
Come on, guys.

00:59:02.300 --> 00:59:04.286
I'm the oldest here...

00:59:12.721 --> 00:59:14.507
Kang Bang Geul.

00:59:16.428 --> 00:59:18.998
Hey, Bang Geul.

00:59:18.998 --> 00:59:20.326
What?

00:59:20.326 --> 00:59:21.626
Why?

00:59:23.225 --> 00:59:25.375
Don't be mad.

00:59:25.375 --> 00:59:27.941
We had no other choice.

00:59:29.156 --> 00:59:31.409
You nearly broke my jaw.

00:59:31.409 --> 00:59:33.808
I'm bruised too. Look.

00:59:33.808 --> 00:59:35.266
Look.

00:59:35.266 --> 00:59:37.001
You...

00:59:37.001 --> 00:59:38.385
Hey!

00:59:38.385 --> 00:59:40.331
I feel bad too.

00:59:41.088 --> 00:59:43.012
Don't brush this off.

00:59:43.012 --> 00:59:47.071
I won't forgive you until you fix this mess.

00:59:50.817 --> 00:59:56.381
Things happen when you work together.

00:59:56.381 --> 00:59:58.245
You're upset?

00:59:58.245 --> 00:59:59.999
So am I!

00:59:59.999 --> 01:00:03.142
You lied that you were Chairman Kang's son.

01:00:03.142 --> 01:00:06.259
Want to settle that today?

01:00:06.259 --> 01:00:09.312
Why bring that up again?

01:00:10.436 --> 01:00:16.356
And you hid that you were his daughter.

01:00:16.356 --> 01:00:19.070
I never got an apology.

01:00:19.070 --> 01:00:22.080
I didn't apologize?

01:00:22.080 --> 01:00:23.900
You didn't.

01:00:23.900 --> 01:00:26.300
Are you sorry or not?

01:00:26.973 --> 01:00:28.185
I'm sorry.

01:00:28.185 --> 01:00:30.017
And you?

01:00:30.017 --> 01:00:31.503
I'm sorry.

01:00:32.729 --> 01:00:36.157
Then have a make-up drink.

01:00:37.411 --> 01:00:40.501
Link arms and drink!

01:00:40.501 --> 01:00:42.424
Do a dare!

01:01:06.002 --> 01:01:08.026
Grandma.

01:01:08.026 --> 01:01:10.032
- Grandma. - Huh?

01:01:15.333 --> 01:01:17.373
Oh, my dear.

01:01:23.810 --> 01:01:25.543
Where are you going?

01:01:26.450 --> 01:01:28.430
Where are you going?

01:01:30.365 --> 01:01:32.158
Jeez.

01:01:32.158 --> 01:01:34.756
Cheers!

01:01:34.756 --> 01:01:36.386
Let's go.

01:01:41.893 --> 01:01:44.120
- Let me pour you one. - Yeah.

01:01:46.092 --> 01:01:47.539
[ICU Alert]

01:01:50.946 --> 01:01:53.923
<i>Code blue, Neurosurgery!</i>

01:01:53.923 --> 01:01:58.236
<i>Neurosurgery team, report to the VIP ICU.</i>

01:02:03.395 --> 01:02:05.999
<i>Code blue, Neurosurgery!</i>

01:02:05.999 --> 01:02:10.112
<i>Neurosurgery team, report to the VIP ICU.</i>

01:02:10.751 --> 01:02:14.577
<i>Code blue, Neurosurgery!</i>

01:02:14.577 --> 01:02:19.586
<i>Neurosurgery team, report to the VIP ICU.</i>

01:02:19.586 --> 01:02:22.189
<i>Code blue, Neurosurgery!</i>

01:02:22.189 --> 01:02:26.095
<i>Neurosurgery team, report to the VIP ICU.</i>

01:02:36.449 --> 01:02:37.913
Drive to the office.

01:02:37.913 --> 01:02:41.310
I'm going to get some sleep. Don't put any calls through.

01:02:41.310 --> 01:02:43.003
Yes, ma'am.

01:03:04.550 --> 01:03:06.055
Hwang Jun Hyeon!

01:03:06.055 --> 01:03:07.794
Jun Hyeon!

01:03:07.794 --> 01:03:10.087
Hey, Hwang Jun Hyeon!

01:03:13.233 --> 01:03:15.518
[Yi Jun's Dad]

01:03:18.419 --> 01:03:19.546
[Professor Min]

01:03:41.908 --> 01:03:42.946
Sir!

01:03:42.946 --> 01:03:45.375
- Calm down... - Move, you bastard!

01:03:51.929 --> 01:03:55.782
Hey, how could you do that?

01:03:56.536 --> 01:04:01.762
How could you kill Father with your own hands?

01:04:10.774 --> 01:04:16.000
[Breaking News: Choiseong Chairman Kang Yong Ho Dies at 72]

01:04:49.876 --> 01:04:52.074
<i>"Protect Choiseong at all costs."</i>

01:04:52.074 --> 01:04:54.775
<i>I'm only doing what Father told me.</i>

01:04:54.775 --> 01:04:56.449
<i>Choiseong changes today.</i>

01:04:56.449 --> 01:04:59.156
<i>Jae Gyeong runs everything now.</i>

01:04:59.156 --> 01:05:00.535
<i>They got a tip.</i>

01:05:00.535 --> 01:05:02.705
<i>Proof she killed Dad.</i>

01:05:02.705 --> 01:05:03.945
<i>The tipster has it.</i>

01:05:03.945 --> 01:05:06.000
<i>I'll set things right.</i>

01:05:06.000 --> 01:05:07.278
<i>I'll give you what you want.</i>

01:05:07.278 --> 01:05:10.362
<i>Tell me what the hell is going on.</i>

01:05:10.362 --> 01:05:12.754
<i>- This isn't right, not between us. - What are we, exactly?</i>

01:05:12.754 --> 01:05:14.115
<i>You can doubt me.</i>

01:05:14.115 --> 01:05:17.382
<i>We'll investigate everything, internally and with prosecutors.</i>

01:05:17.382 --> 01:05:19.708
<i>Stop bothering me and get out!</i>

01:05:20.795 --> 01:05:22.725
<i>Where are you?</i>

01:05:22.725 --> 01:05:25.078
<i>No way, Bang Geul!</i>

